
DATE  : May 29, 2022

1. I have been using random Sub name in the study notes.
2. Sub name is important as it will define the action.

   (Example 1)
   Private Sub Worksheet_Activate()
   --> Codes will be processed upon activating the worksheet.
   
   (Example 2)
   Sub Button1_Click()
   --> Codes will be processed upon clicking the button.

   
